data.description: Welcome to this stunning two-story home with a versatile floor plan, boasting 4 bedrooms, 3 baths, and a game room. Located in desirable Lost Creek Neighborhood in Boerne. Unbelievably priced at an amazing 140.64 per square foot!  This spacious property features an island kitchen with double ovens. Second Master suite conveniently situated downstairs provides both privacy and functionality.  As you enter, you'll be greeted by an inviting foyer that leads you to the heart of the home. The open-concept living area seamlessly connects the kitchen, dining area, and family room, creating an ideal space for entertaining guests or spending quality time with family. The island kitchen showcases Granite countertops, modern appliances, rich hardwood cabinetry, and a breakfast bar.  Plush wood floors in family Room and formal dining area.  Venture upstairs to discover the remaining bedrooms, including a spacious primary suite. The primary bedroom offers a serene escape with a generous walk-in closet and a luxurious en-suite bathroom featuring a soaking tub, separate shower, and dual sinks. Two additional well-appointed bedrooms and a shared bath complete the second level.  The game room provides an additional living space, which can be utilized as a playroom, media room, a perfect space for relaxation.  Its versatility allows for endless possibilities and ensures everyone has their own area to unwind.  Outside, the backyard offers a large, covered patio and oversized deck with pergola. The yard is framed with beautiful mature trees providing privacy and just the right amount of shade.    This home is conveniently located near schools, shopping centers, parks, and major transportation routes. Don't miss the chance to make this impeccable residence your new home. Schedule a showing today and experience the beauty and functionality this property has to offer.
